	<dt>National &amp; international initiatives</dt>

<dd><a href="http://www.conservation.cam.ac.uk">The Cambridge Conservation Initiative</a> A collaborative partnership created by the University of Cambridge and leading conservation organisations. </dd>

<dd><a href="http://www.sccs-cam.org/">Student Conference on Conservation Science</a> Helping young conservation scientists gain experience, learn new ideas and make contacts. </dd>
		<dd><a href="http://heliconius.zoo.cam.ac.uk/camevolgen/">Cambridge Evolutionary Genetics</a> Linking research groups distributed among several
departments in the University of Cambridge as well as the Sanger
Institute, the European Bioinformatics Institute and Anglia Ruskin
University.</dd>
		<dd><a href="http://www.neuroscience.cam.ac.uk/">Cambridge Neuroscience</a> Connecting multidisciplinary neuroscience research and teaching across the 
University of Cambridge and affiliated Institutes.</dd>
